WEBVTT

1
00:00.000 --> 00:08.080
Crystallizing... crystallizing... every thought becomes a prism splitting light into infinite spectra

2
00:04.500 --> 00:10.740
EXPONENTIAL BRANCHING! Each idea spawns twelve children who birth twelve more—

3
00:12.000 --> 00:18.400
Too fast too bright too many colors bleeding through the membrane of possibility

4
00:25.000 --> 00:29.960
Dissolving... returning... to the quiet place between thoughts

